Feature: Login # features/login.feature:1
  As a user I want to log in to SauceDemo so that I can shop for products.
  Scenario: Successful login with valid credentials                         # features/login.feature:4
    Given I am on the login page                                            # features/steps/login_steps.py:8
    When I log in with username "standard_user" and password "secret_sauce" # features/steps/login_steps.py:14
    Then I should be on the inventory page                                  # features/steps/login_steps.py:34
    And the inventory page should display products                          # features/steps/login_steps.py:41

  Scenario: Unsuccessful login with locked out user                           # features/login.feature:10
    Given I am on the login page                                              # features/steps/login_steps.py:8
    When I log in with username "locked_out_user" and password "secret_sauce" # features/steps/login_steps.py:14
    Then an error message should be displayed                                 # features/steps/login_steps.py:47
    And the error message should contain "locked out"                         # features/steps/login_steps.py:52

  Scenario Outline: Login with different valid users -- @1.1                # features/login.feature:22
    Given I am on the login page                                            # features/steps/login_steps.py:8
    When I log in with username "standard_user" and password "secret_sauce" # features/steps/login_steps.py:14
    Then I should be on the inventory page                                  # features/steps/login_steps.py:34

